      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for simulation must be verified and under version control with documented test cases.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2021 R2 used with FDA-validated benchmark suite. Version control via Git; automated regression tests confirm solver outputs against analytic solutions for beam bending and contact problems. SQA plan documented and reviewed by independent engineer."
    },
    {
