      "rationale": "Euler-Bernoulli and Timoshenko beam benchmarks reproduced to within 0.5% of analytic solutions. Contact patch test passed. Nonlinear material benchmark (bilinear isotropic hardening) agrees with closed-form solution to within 1.2%."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
