      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model input parameters match experimental conditions used in validation testing.",
      "rationale": "Material properties, geometry, boundary conditions, and loading parameters in the FEA model confirmed to match the as-tested experimental configuration. Traceability matrix linking each model input to its experimental counterpart reviewed and approved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
