      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric defined a priori; acceptance bounds pre-specified; comparison performed for all primary QoIs.",
      "rationale": "Acceptance bounds defined a priori: percent error <10% and E/uval <1.96 for all QoIs. Stiffness: 4.2% error, E/uval=0.87. Yield force: 6.8% error, E/uval=1.41. Force at 40 mm: 7.3% error. All within bounds. Comparison documented in validation report VR-2023-001."
    },
