      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and directly relevant to the clinical performance claim. These QoIs are used in the 510(k) submission to demonstrate mechanical equivalence to predicate device."
