      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities reproduce the physics, geometry, and loading conditions of the COU with documented similarity assessment.",
      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 bench test replicates the mechanical loading environment of the lumbar spine construct in a standardised, reproducible manner. Similarity assessment documented: loading mode (compression-bending), construct geometry, and fixation block material all matched to clinical COU. Physiological aspects (bone quality, in vivo loads) not replicated but acknowledged as scope limitation addressed by conservative test configuration."
